<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <% include ../static/partials/head.ejs %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include ../static/partials/navbar.ejs %>
    <section class="container">
      <% include ../static/partials/messages.ejs %>
      <h2 style="padding-top: 25px">Special request</h2>
      <h5 style="padding-top: 12px">
        Dear Traveler, welcome to Capacity. The new platform connecting you to
        the main jet operators from Europe and America, offering their empty-leg
        charter flights.
      </h5>
      <p class="question">
        Not found what you were looking for in our listings?
      </p>
      <p>
        At Capacity, our dedicated team can work the extra mile upon your
        request.<br />
        Thanks to our extended network among jet operators, we can research the
        flight which might suit your needs. <br />
        Just let us know by submitting your request in the below form. If a
        full-fare flight might also suits you, please let us know.
      </p>
      <p>
        Should you be interested in sending us your request, you'll need to
        sign-in or sign-up below
      </p>
      <form action="/client" id="contact-form" method="post" role="form">
          <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input
            id="name"
            name="name"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Your name"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input
            id="email"
            name="email"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Your email"
            required
          />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
          <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
          <input
            id="phone"
            name="phone"
            type="tel"
            placeholder="Your phone number"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea
            id="message"
            name="message"
            placeholder="Enter your message here"
            rows="3"
            required
          >
          </textarea>
        </div>
          <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </fieldset>
      </form>
      <% include ../static/partials/baseScripts.ejs %>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
